<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .alert { color: #d9534f; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>New Login Detected</h2>
        <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>We detected a new login to your account from a new device:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Device:</strong> <%= deviceName %></li>
            <li><strong>Type:</strong> <%= deviceType %></li>
            <li><strong>Time:</strong> <%= time %></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="alert">If this was you, you can ignore this email. If you don't recognize this activity, please change your password immediately.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
